### `Error: Route "/path" used \`cookies()\`/\`headers()\` without \`await\``
**Cause**: Next.js 15 made `cookies()` and `headers()` async
```typescript
// ❌ BROKEN (Next.js 14 syntax, breaks in 15)
const cookieStore = cookies()

// ✅ FIX
const cookieStore = await cookies()
const headersList = await headers()
```

