### `TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'user')`
**Cause**: Accessing auth user before session loads, or in a Server Component without awaiting
```typescript
// ❌ BROKEN
const { data } = supabase.auth.getUser()  // missing await

// ✅ FIX
const { data: { user }, error } = await supabase.auth.getUser()
if (error || !user) redirect('/login')
```

