### Build error: `Type error: Property 'X' does not exist on type 'Y'`
**Cause**: TypeScript type mismatch — common in Rocket-generated Supabase query results
```typescript
// ✅ FIX — type the Supabase response
type Profile = {
  id: string
  display_name: string | null
  avatar_url: string | null
  created_at: string
}

const { data: profile, error } = await supabase
  .from('profiles')
  .select('*')
  .eq('id', user.id)
  .single<Profile>()  // add generic type
```

