### `AuthSessionMissingError: Auth session missing!`
**Cause**: Trying to use server Supabase client without a valid session cookie
```typescript
// ✅ FIX — always check before using session
const { data: { user }, error } = await supabase.auth.getUser()
if (error || !user) {
  // Handle gracefully — don't crash
  redirect('/login')
}
```

