### OAuth redirect: `Redirect URL mismatch` / blank page after Google login
**Cause**: Callback URL in provider console or Supabase doesn't match app URL
```
✅ FIX checklist:
1. Supabase Dashboard → Auth → URL Configuration → add:
   - http://localhost:3000/auth/callback
   - https://your-app.netlify.app/auth/callback
   - https://your-custom-domain.com/auth/callback

2. Google Cloud Console → Authorized redirect URIs → add:
   https://[project-id].supabase.co/auth/v1/callback

3. Make sure app/auth/callback/route.ts exists and calls:
   supabase.auth.exchangeCodeForSession(code)
```

