## ⚡ STRIPE ERRORS

### `StripeSignatureVerificationError: No signatures found matching the expected signature for payload`
**Cause**: Request body parsed as JSON before signature verification (destroys raw body)
```typescript
// ❌ BROKEN — destroys raw body
const body = await request.json()  // NEVER do this for webhooks

// ✅ FIX — use raw text
const body = await request.text()  // preserves raw bytes for signature check
const sig = request.headers.get('stripe-signature')!
const event = stripe.webhooks.constructEvent(body, sig, process.env.STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET!)
```

